org.cpsolver.coursett.model

Class Configuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.coursett.model.Configuration

  • public class Configuration
extends Object
    Configuration. Each course can have multiple configurations. A student needs to be enrolled into classes of one of the configurations.
